comments: Banchero (ORL) is moving alongside Randle's (NYK) path and marginal body contact occurs during Randle's (NYK) drive.
Banchero (ORL) contests Hart's (NYK) driving shot attempt and marginal body contact occurs.
Fultz (ORL) firms up in a screening position in Randle's (NYK) path and incidental upper body contact occurs.
Randle (NYK) reaches in and initiates contact to Banchero's (ORL) front that affects his SQBR during the drive.
Harris (ORL) extends both hands forward and initiates contact with Randle (NYK), which affects his SQBR.
Banchero (ORL) briefly places his hands on Grimes (NYK) before releasing.
Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in Grimes's (NYK) path and marginal contact occurs as he releases to the rim.
Banchero (ORL) briefly places an arm to Quickley's (NYK) front and the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Grimes (NYK) maintains a legal guarding position while defending Fultz (ORL).
Banchero (ORL) moves forward into Hart (NYK) while he is airborne and initiates contact that affects his ability to return to the floor.
Grimes (NYK) extends both hands forward and initiates contact with Fultz (ORL) during the drive, affecting his SQBR.
Randle (NYK) establishes himself in Fultz's (ORL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Carter Jr. (ORL) legally contests Hart's (NYK) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Grimes (NYK) brings both hands toward Fultz (ORL) but the contact is marginal as he is able to release the pass.
Hart (NYK) commits a take foul on Banchero (ORL).
Anthony (ORL) brings both hands toward Randle (NYK) and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Randle (NYK) briefly brings his off-arm toward Anthony (ORL) and releases away as marginal contact occurs prior to his gather.
Anthony (ORL) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Randle's (NYK) arm.
